| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-0728 — Mass File Rename (lynx)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 0023b294-77ed-5c05-904f-dc2ed28af564"
index=*
| where (file_path="*.encrypted" OR file_path="*.locked" OR file_path="*.ransom")
